'''Tufya''' neɣ '''Affay''' tigawt tarmerrayt iswi-ynes d taččarit n [[Turin]] s [[azwu|wezwu]] n [[Uksijin|O²]] ar wesɣel afellay. Anda amdan ad yeldi [[imi|imi-s]] s waṭas alamma yuɣal ubleɣ [[Tankart|tenkart-is]] yugar 4 n tikkal n ubelɣ-is aẓaṛan. Tuffya tettaṭṭaf azal n 6 n [[Tasint|tsinin]] deg wkud-a yettili-d waqqaf n [[tamaẓwalt|tmaẓwalin]] n [[udem|wudem]] d [[iri (agman)|yiri]] akken i d-yettili daɣen wergal (amdal) n [[tiṭṭ|wallen]], S wanect-a [[Aramas|isalan iramasen]] yakk ttbaddiden (ḥebbsen) i kra n wakud anda yettuɣal ur yettefray ara (ur yettḥulfu ara) i wayen i d-as-yezzin. Tissugent s usemres n [[Tanzayt|usɣiwes amsisli]] n [[aqziz|yiqzaz]] tessken-d d akken iqzaz deg wadis n yemma-s d win yettfayen s waṭas ɣas akken ur [[asgunef|yettsugefaw]] ara s turin

