== Isragen (ssebbat) n tufya ==
Ar tura isragen i d-igellun s tufya zeddiɣ-it (mazal) ur ttwassnen ara, yerna aṭas n imusnawen ukzen-d (steɛrfen-d) d akken taluft-a ur sekfin ara azref-is deg tezrawt d unagi. Maca llan waṭas n isegza i tumant n tufya, gar-asent:
* Kra n imessujiyen ttɣilen d akken tufya tettili-d mi ara ad yili weswir n [[Uksijin|weksujin]] (''O²'') d adersi deg [[tafekka|tfekka]] yerna aswir n [[asinuksid n ukaṛbun|usinuksid n ukaṛbun]] (''Co²'') d win yilin, Dɣa assegzi ayyi iga d imezdi 
* Kra n imessujiyen niden ttɣilen d akken tufya d tigawt tamulit iy teggẓen [[turin]] seg ukucam
* [[Hipukrat]] yessegzaw-d d akken tufya tzerreb azwu yumsen seg turin akken i yettarra aktum n [[idammen]] ɣer [[Allaɣ|wallaɣ]] 

